From Ken K Subject Re IIsi question The si has a single expansion slot that can be either PDS or Nubus but not both The card lies parallel to and above the motherboard HD and requires an adaptor slot to do There are Nubus and PDS adaptort Thus what kind of slots you have depends on what kind of adapter card you With the exception of the Radius rocket all NuBus cards I know of work in the PDS slots and thus cards are Mac specific thus not all PDS cards work in all From Planet BMUG the FirstClass BBS of The message contained in this posting does not in any way reflect BMUG's official